<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">غ ي د:</span> <span class="c2">(الْغَيَدُ)</span> بِفَتْحَتَيْنِ النُّعُومَةُ وَامْرَأَةٌ <span class="c2">(غَيْدَاءُ)</span> وَ <span class="c2">(غَادَةٌ)</span> أَيْ نَاعِمَةٌ. وَ <span class="c2">(الْأَغْيَدُ)</span> الْوَسْنَانُ الْمَائِلُ الْعُنُقِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>